sections.text: Label as warranty3-274.Label as warrantyAny label or descriptive tag attached to a lot, parcel or package of commercial fertilizer, agricultural mineral or other fertilizer material carrying a chemical analysis or claims for other values shall be deemed a warranty as to the things stated thereon by the person attaching the label or tag in favor of the buyer and of each successive buyer purchasing the goods relying thereon.
